{"tid":439649,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李飛指噓國歌違基本法危害國家 追溯與否視乎人大決定","createTime":"2017-10-18T03:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T08:51:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cac6791b89573fe511ae0ac11ce4110a5975d291","tid":439649,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"本港將要因應內地通過的《國歌法》而訂立相關本地法例，特首林鄭月娥昨指本港法例並非很多有追溯期，但例如印花稅修訂草案就有，被批評以民事條例類比國歌法的刑事法例是「不知所謂」。港澳辦前主任王光亞昨明言噓國歌是嚴重違法，今日他再指「對於任何一個國家的國民來說，尊重國家、國歌和國旗，是基本要求」。至於國歌法是否有追溯期，王光亞認為香港可以根據本身的法治制度來考慮。<br />\n<br />\n同樣在北京的基本法委員會主任李飛表示，噓國歌的行為違反基本法、危害國家，下一次全國人大常委會，即明年3月，將會通過將國歌法列入基本法附件三，到時一切會根據有關決定。民主派已計劃就《國歌法》本地立法在立法會提休會辯論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57346128&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57346128%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171018&d=u3ii42TOxFjH6%2FPSemRc49Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=9137b119\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57346128%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171018&h=951c2913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57346128&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171018</a>"},{"pid":"60990ad9dfbb3a6192ac4a2b99af958240713479","tid":439649,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfbf11d4bee109f136c46392a8470f6ebd70167","tid":439649,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果膠袋稅有追溯期<br />\n係咪話膠袋稅都有得追溯，噓都應該有"},{"pid":"e707e038c9af8df4d3617e35f6e0391bfa75aca0","tid":43964